  "flow": {
    "actions": [
      {
        "id": "json",
        "title": {
          "en": "Insert JSON into database"
        },
        "titleFormatted": {
          "en": "Insert [[json]] into [[database]]"
        },
        "hint": {
          "en": "Uses JSON.parse to evaluate the argument.\n\nConsider a database with 3 columns: Name (a title type), Age (a number type) and Occupation (a text type). An example input would look like this:\n\n{\n  \"Name\": \"My Name\",\n  \"Age\": 10,\n  \"Occupation\": \"Astronaut\"\n}\n\nOther supported types:\n\nStatus e.g. \"MyStatus\": \"MyOption\"\nCheckbox e.g \"MyCheckbox\": true"
        },
        "args": [
          {
            "type": "device",
            "name": "device",
            "filter": "driver_id=user"
          },
          {
            "type": "autocomplete",
            "name": "database",
            "title": {
              "en": "Database"
            },
            "placeholder": {
              "en": "My Database"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "name": "json",
            "title": {
              "en": "JSON"
            },
            "placeholder": {
              "en": "{ \"field\": \"value\" }"
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "query",
        "title": {
          "en": "Query a database"
        },
        "titleFormatted": {
          "en": "Query [[database]] [[filter]] [[sorts]]"
        },
        "hint": {
          "en": "Uses JSON.parse to evaluate the filter argument.\n\nThe JSON representation of this filter configuration looks like this:\n\n{\n  \"and\": [\n    {\n      \"property\": \"Done\",\n      \"checkbox\": {\n        \"equals\": true\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"or\": [\n        {\n          \"property\": \"Tags\",\n          \"contains\": \"A\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"property\": \"Tags\",\n          \"contains\": \"B\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nFor all possible options see the link below.\n\nhttps://developers.notion.com/reference/post-database-query-filter"
        },
        "args": [
          {
            "type": "device",
            "name": "device",
            "filter": "driver_id=user"
          },
          {
            "type": "autocomplete",
            "name": "database",
            "title": {
              "en": "Database"
            },
            "placeholder": {
              "en": "My Database"
            }
          },
          {
            "required": false,
            "type": "text",
            "name": "filter",
            "title": {
              "en": "Filter"
            },
            "placeholder": {
              "en": "{ \"field\": \"value\" }"
            }
          },
          {
            "required": false,
            "type": "text",
            "name": "sorts",
            "title": {
              "en": "Sorts"
            },
            "placeholder": {
              "en": "[{\n  \"property\": \"Last ordered\",\n  \"direction\": \"ascending\"\n}]"
            }
          }
        ],
        "tokens": [
          {
            "name": "response",
            "type": "string",
            "title": {
              "en": "Result"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
